WEBVTT

00:00.050 --> 00:04.039
Samsung Electronics provides many social benefits for its employees free of charge.

00:04.315 --> 00:07.158
As the welfare state in South Korea is only slowly emerging,...

00:07.411 --> 00:10.798
...Samsung Electronics stands out as an attractive and reliable employer...

00:10.921 --> 00:14.480
...with its broad offering of free social services in Samsung Digital City.

00:14.939 --> 00:18.095
These services include health care, child care, free food,...

00:18.271 --> 00:20.512
...recreation and free public transportation.

00:20.919 --> 00:24.189
In case you need to see a doctor during your stay in Samsung Digital City,...

00:24.434 --> 00:26.758
...it is entirely free for Samsung employees.

00:27.157 --> 00:29.767
The health care service is free at Samsung Digital City...

00:29.885 --> 00:33.761
...with numerous medical facilities that offer everything from physicals and flu shots...

00:33.853 --> 00:36.032
...to dental treatments and traditional acupuncture.

00:36.735 --> 00:40.659
Samsung Digital City has 10 basketball courts, four badminton courts,...

00:40.776 --> 00:43.144
...three soccer fields, two baseball diamonds,...

00:43.259 --> 00:45.731
...a climbing wall and an Olympic-size swimming pool.

00:46.085 --> 00:50.865
It also serves up to 72,000 meals with 92 different menus daily.

00:51.173 --> 00:53.869
The cafeteria with more than 4,100 seats...

00:53.988 --> 00:56.188
...sources its produce from Suwon's neighborhoods,...

00:56.295 --> 00:59.000
...creating a strong link with farmers and producers.

